    rdfs:label "Sub-series consists of records providing information about the artworks contained within sub-series F 47-11-1 to F 47-11-3. It is not clear whether Elizabeth Simcoe was the author of these documents. Two are caption lists of some of her sketches; the remaining two documents are scraps, containing a few names and notes. There is also a map indicating places where Elizabeth Simcoe made sketches." .

